text: This game was a very good and addicting take on the Tetris formula. I think this particular theme was hidden because I never heard it while playing the game and it's very different from the rest of the downbeat/techno soundtrack. Back in the late 90s when most of﻿ the game music I had on my computer were Midis, I had an unnamed midi of this track and I really liked it. I just recently discovered it was from this game. I even made a cover back in 2007 when I was learning how to use FL Studio!
